commentText: Unit test for SPR-13747 - ensures that reverse lookup of media type from media_type key is case-insensitive.
codeText: @Test_	public void lookupMediaTypeCaseInsensitive() {_		Map<String, MediaType> mapping = Collections.singletonMap("json", MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON)__		MappingMediaTypeFileExtensionResolver resolver = new MappingMediaTypeFileExtensionResolver(mapping)__		MediaType mediaType = resolver.lookupMediaType("JSON")___		assertEquals(mediaType, MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON)__	}
